{"tid":1293502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實 依家黑警惡撚到咁 仲有咩方法可以制裁佢地...","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:07:18.000Z","uid":47024,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"366aeee3c2813e6e8b439531fb2ef9b105cfba81","tid":1293502,"uid":47024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"一開facebook<br />\n成版都係黑警冇委任證 亂打人<br />\n有d仲要連制服都冇撚著<br />\n隻白衫狗仲癲撚到<br />\n可以當住鏡頭話一個人show委任證<br />\n就可以代表晒成個場嘅警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家黑警已經走火入魔<br />\n連做show都唔撚柒做<br />\n擺撚到明係恃住拎住著槍<br />\n乜撚野規則都唔使理<br />\n依家警犬根本同軍政府冇分別<br />\n<br />\n去到呢個地步<br />\n除左武裝革命同佢搏命<br />\n仲有冇方法可以制止佢地...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉屌 睇撚到好撚灰 好撚無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d451c0a6501683b3ac2b9df40c4e2d1a679d864b","tid":1293502,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29fea7e511a6f9a682567921d548e58c850adbb1","tid":1293502,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無</span><br />\n<br />\n無論事成與否，無論政制外定政制內都耐呢班畜生唔何"},{"pid":"3518210c0dddfc9bec61900550473cb5c1d26c9d","tid":1293502,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"場仗未打完架！五大訴求未接納，一眾被捕士未釋放，林鄭未鞠躬，盧偉聰未落台，外國戰線啱啱先開始(在此向攬炒巴致敬)，現階段邊個同政府對話邊個就係鬼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEbbGfV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEbbGfV.jpg&h=252d433f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AMfoug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMfoug.jpg&h=5527c394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qANusVW.jpg\" data-thumb